:: ROUTE_1_02 {"position":"525,700","size":"100,100"}
(set: $typewriterText to "Basically I'm from Kashmir, the part of - you know - Pakistan, because Kashmir is divided in two parts.
                                                                                        
One is in under the control of India and one is under the control of Pakistan. 
                    
So basically I'm from Kashmir, Pakistan. ")

