:: ROUTE_1_03 {"position":"675,700","size":"100,100"}
(set: $typewriterText to "When I start the work, so I came to the train station in Domodossola,                                                     when I exit that train station,                                                       so I login in my application and then I was, you know, waiting for the orders.                                                         
So it's the online system.                   

So whenever the order will come,                                            so I have to go for the pick up the order and then I need to go to the customer address.                                        
So the whole day like you know this.                        So we are basically not sitting in a one place. ")

{
  
  (set: $typewriterPos to 1)


