:: ROUTE_1_04 {"position":"825,700","size":"100,100"}
(set: $typewriterText to "So if I'm sitting here for example,       so 10-15 minutes or 20 minutes, I will see that order is not coming.                                                                         
So I will move to the another place.                                                          
                           
So in the whole day we are basically, you know, the running in the whole Milan that for finding the orders.                                                                              

So this is the thing in the lunch time we have a little bit of work                   and like you know, like 12 to midday, 12:00 to 2:00 we have the work.                     
So two to six we don't have the much work.  ")

